# Non-secret environment config for the ironboi-staging project.
# Loaded automatically by firebase-tools at `firebase deploy --only functions`.
# Secrets (GEMINI_API_KEY) stay in Secret Manager via defineSecret — never here.

# Gemini function-calling tool loop (adapt_plan / accept / reject /
# ask_follow_up_question). ON for staging as of 2026-07-14. When this is
